    "description": "In each level you have the task to catch a certain amount of the moving dots by starting a chain reaction. Choose wisely where to start it!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>105 varied levels<br></li><li>up to 1000 dots per level</li></ul><br>6 different types of special dots, each with special abilities for new fun:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>white dots: you get an extra starting shot<br></li><li>blue dots: remain permanent and the other dots bounce off<br></li><li>orange dots: remain permanent and the other dots explode on them<br></li><li>green dots: you have to catch these dots to complete the level<br></li><li>purple dots: change the physics of the game<br></li><li>red dots: you must not catch these dots, because... you'll see :-)</li></ul><br>Additional content: finish all levels and unlock the ultimate hard mode!",
